<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <!-- 
      This is the main Handlebars template for the site 
      - When the user visits the homepage or submits a color the app calls the endpoints in server.js
      - The server script passes data in here and the Handlebars code builds it into the HTML page
    -->

    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="https://glitch.com/favicon.ico" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <title>{{seo.title}}</title>

    <!-- Meta tags for SEO and social sharing -->
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{seo.url}}">
    <meta name="description" content="{{seo.description}}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{seo.title}}">
    <meta property="og:type" content="article">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{seo.url}}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{seo.description}}">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{seo.image}}">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">

</head>

<body>


    <!-- Menu -->
    {{> menu }}
    <!-- Menu -->


    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="content" role="main">

            <!-- This is the start of content for our page -->

            <div class="container mx-auto">

                <div class="bg-white h-5/5 px-9 py-9">

                    <p class="text-4xl font-light ">Customer Service</p>

                    <p class="text-4xl font-bold pb-4">Do you need help ? </p>

                    <p class="leading-8 text-gray-500 mt-8"> If you didn't know this form will create a ticket and then the ticket will be analyzed and categorized based on the body of the request. 
                        Indeed if the request contains words like "billing", this ticket will have the "billing issue" category. 
                        This is pretty cool and this shows how powerful can be service hub. 
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-gray-500"> This form submission is set to create a ticket</p>

                </div>


                <section class="px-9 py-9">
                    <script charset="utf-8" type="text/javascript" src="//js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js"></script>
                    <script>
                        hbspt.forms.create({
                            region: "na1",
                            portalId: "21250603",
                            formId: "eda04a6a-7cba-43a7-a028-d18cc04878f0"
                        });
                    </script>
                </section>


            </div>


        </div>
    </div>

</body>



<!-- footer -->
{{> footer }}
<!-- footer -->

</html>